# Welcome

Erlware provides a community for erlang oriented open source projects. The [Erlware projects]({relocatable:/tools}) are defined by there transparent, community based development process and liberal license. We hope to foster a community of accomplished dedicated open source developers that provide projects and tools that the Erlang community sorely needs.

# Latest News

Dave Peticolas has taken over maintainership of erlware-mode. Our homegrown emacs mode for Erlang!

